These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-1::.
City: berlin, liverpool, hannover
1. City:liverpool is on the right of City:hannover##1
2. City:berlin is on the far right##1
3. City:berlin is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |   3   |
| City   | hannover | liverpool | berlin |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-2::.
Music-Genre: jazz, trance, folk
1. Music-Genre:trance is in an odd position##4
2. Music-Genre:jazz is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | jazz | folk | trance |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-3::.
Nationality: argentine, canadian, japanese
1. Nationality:canadian is in an even position##4
2. Nationality:canadian is on the left or right of Nationality:japanese##3
3. Nationality:japanese is on the right of Nationality:canadian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3       |
| Nationality   | argentine | canadian | japanese |

 #################################
 
